data.description: Nestled within a serene and enchanting woodland setting, this captivating residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and natural beauty. The charming exterior, characterized by its timeless architecture, stands proudly on a spacious wooded lot, providing an immediate sense of tranquility and privacy. Stepping through the front door, you're greeted by the warmth of the wood floors that span throughout the main living areas. Sunlight pours in through large windows, casting a gentle glow that highlights the intricate grain of the wood and infuses the space with a cozy ambiance. The open layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and the updated kitchen, creating an inviting space for both intimate gatherings and larger celebrations. The kitchen, a true masterpiece, boasts modern amenities and sleek design offering ample space for culinary creations. Stainless steel appliances glisten under the soft lighting, The four bedrooms are thoughtfully positioned, providing optimal privacy and comfort. Each room boasts large windows that frame views of the surrounding greenery, inviting the outdoors in and creating a soothing atmosphere. The wood floors continue into these spaces, enhancing the sense of unity throughout the home. A highlight of this exquisite property is the inviting pool area. Step outside onto the wooden deck that wraps around the crystal-clear waters of the pool. Whether you're seeking a refreshing swim on a warm day or simply wish to bask in the sun's embrace, this oasis offers a retreat from the everyday hustle and bustle.
